</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Avertisseur sonore (dans le combiné des instruments) 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Chaque témoin 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarme du mode d&#39;allumage non renvoyée 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Le mode d&#39;allumage est en position &#34;ACC&#34; alors que la porte conducteur est ouverte. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Intermittent 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarme du mode d&#39;allumage 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Un des contacteurs de demande de porte est enfoncé alors que le mode d&#39;allumage est en position &#34;ACC&#34; ou &#34;ON&#34;, le dispositif de commande à distance se trouve à l&#39;extérieur du véhicule et toutes les portes sont fermées. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Une fois (2 s) 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarme 1 de porte ouverte 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Un des contacteurs de demande de porte est enfoncé alors qu&#39;une des portes est ouverte et que le mode d&#39;allumage est en position &#34;OFF&#34;. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Une fois (2 s) 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarme 2 de porte ouverte 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Les portes sont verrouillées avec le système d&#39;ouverture sans clé alors qu&#39;une des portes est ouverte et que le mode d&#39;allumage est en position &#34;OFF&#34;. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarme de prévention de verrouillage du dispositif de commande à distance 1 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Un des contacteurs de demande de porte est enfoncé alors que le mode d&#39;allumage est en position &#34;OFF&#34;, le dispositif de commande à distance se trouve dans l&#39;habitacle du véhicule ou dans le compartiment à bagages et toutes les portes sont fermées. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Une fois (2 s) 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarme de prévention de verrouillage du dispositif de commande à distance 2 (si le véhicule en est équipé) 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Le bouton &#34;Lock&#34; du dispositif de commande à distance est enfoncé alors que le mode d&#39;allumage est en position &#34;OFF&#34;, le dispositif de commande à distance est dans l&#39;habitacle ou dans le compartiment à bagages, et les portes du conducteur et du passager sont fermées. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Une fois (2 s) 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarme de batterie du dispositif de commande à distance déchargée *1 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Le dispositif de commande à distance envoie un signal de batterie du dispositif de commande à distance déchargée au module de commande de démarrage sans clé alors que le mode d&#39;allumage est en position &#34;ON&#34;. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Le témoin de déchargement de pile de dispositif de commande à distance s&#39;allume (15 s) 
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarme de dispositif de commande à distance hors de la zone de détection *2 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Il n&#39;y a pas de dispositif de commande à distance enregistré dans l&#39;habitacle du véhicule lorsque le contacteur du moteur est enfoncé alors que le mode d&#39;allumage est en position &#34;OFF&#34;. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
*1 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Le témoin de dispositif antidémarrage s&#39;allume (5 s) 
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Le témoin PUSH clignote 
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarme d&#39;anomalie du verrouillage de direction 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
La porte du conducteur est ouverte avec le verrouillage de direction déverrouillé alors que le mode d&#39;allumage est en position &#34;ACC&#34; ou qu&#39;il est passé de &#34;ON &#34; à &#34;OFF&#34;. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Intermittent 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Le témoin de dispositif antidémarrage s&#39;allume 
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarme de dispositif de commande à distance emporté 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Le dispositif de commande à distance est emporté hors du véhicule, une des portes est ouverte, puis toutes les portes sont fermées alors que le mode d&#39;allumage est en position &#34;ON&#34; ou &#34;ACC&#34;. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
5 fois 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
5 fois 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Le témoin de dispositif antidémarrage s&#39;allume 
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Le témoin PUSH clignote 
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Le dispositif de commande à distance est emporté hors du véhicule et le contacteur du moteur est enfoncé avec la pédale d&#39;embrayage enfoncée alors que le mode d&#39;allumage est en position &#34;ON&#34; ou &#34;ACC&#34;. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Alarme de dysfonctionnement du système 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Le dysfonctionnement est détecté dans le système de démarrage sans clé. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
— 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Le témoin de dispositif antidémarrage s&#39;allume 
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Le témoin de système antivol clignote 
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
